---
title: Creamy Mushroom Gnocchi with Pine Nuts & Parmesan
description: This mellow combination of buttery mushrooms, fragrant onions and baby spinach makes this meal homey and comforting. Tossed through golden pan-fried gnocchi and topped with toasted pine nuts, here's a moreish bowl you won't be able to resist!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b70ff6d30006c4a5367e134-498f2a71.jpg
